attributes.title: Some problems
attributes.review: Okay, serious review here. I wanted to download the app to see who everyone’s plans are, and what everyone was about because I’ll be able to vote this election so I wanted an educated vote. Although my personal opinion of Trump isn’t great, I still wanted to see and form a “factual” opinion. But, when I opened the app, it kept crashing every time I tried to sign up. THEN, I wasn’t even able to open the app without it straight up crashing without me even be able to see anything on the app. Kind of disappointed😔
